messages.message:
@tony.shi just merged in a huge PR that bumps protobuf version from v3 to v4
https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/73910

This remove 130k+ lines of code!!

Posting as an FYI - if you encounter any issues, please let us know. Also be mindful to ensure that there is no big diff when you make any proto changes.
Model service is currently having issues due to the use of some deprecated fields, but I'm working on a follow up PR!
Temporary fix is here (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/73917) if anyone needs to cherry-pick this to continue using model service. Will merge once the CIs complete
